text: Harry is the surname of: * Bill Harry (born 1938), creator of the newspaper Mersey Beat * Debbie Harry (born 1945), American singer-songwriter and actress * J. S. Harry (1939-2015), Australian poet * John Harry (cricketer) (1857–1919), Australian cricketer * John Harry (MP) (fl. 1410), MP for Hastings * N'Keal Harry (born 1997), American football player * Robert Harry I, MP for Winchelsea in 1373 and 1382 * Robert Harry II, MP for Seaford in 1397 and 1399 * Troels Harry (born 1990), Danish curler
title: Harry (surname)
